// Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2025-0747 — Mass File Rename (anubis)
// Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 986bd2be-9842-5759-80ab-dc601238b426

#event_simpleName=*
| (FilePath = *.encrypted OR FilePath = *.locked OR FilePath = *.ransom)
| table([timestamp, ComputerName])
| limit(1000)
